msgid "KDiskFree"
msgstr "KDiskFree"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.kdf.appdata.xml:10
msgid "View Disk Usage"
msgstr "Tampilan Penggunaan Disk"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.kdf.appdata.xml:12
msgid ""
"KDiskFree displays the available file devices (hard drive partitions, floppy "
"and CD drives, etc.) along with information on their capacity, free space, "
"type and mount point. It also allows you to mount and unmount drives and "
"view them in a file manager."
msgstr ""
"KDiskFree menampilkan peranti file yang tersedia (partisi hard drive, floppy "
"dan drive CD, dll.) bersama dengan informasi tentang kapasitas, ruang "
"kosong, jenis dan titik kaitnya. Ini juga memungkinkan kamu untuk mengait "
"dan melepas drive dan melihatnya di file manager."

